Recorded with Voice Memos app on iPhone SE (second generation) with internal microphone facing the bird.

Recording made with Voice Memos app on iPhone internal mic with audio compression enabled (apologies). Bird was perched on a fallen trunk about a metre off the ground and about 5 metres away from mic, in deep shade in hilly secondary forest in fair weather. Another rooster can be heard calling from far away in alternation. No trimming of recording so time intervals between calls are actual.
